This repository hosts release artifacts (DMG files, appcast.xml, README) for
CookPlanStudio. The release artifacts are provided for installation use only;
redistribution, decompilation, or reverse-engineering of the bundled
CookPlanStudio.app is not permitted.

No source code is included in this repository. CookPlanStudio's source is
maintained in a private repository.
